  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Turquoise Mountain Trust</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Since 2006, Turquoise Mountain has worked to develop skills and jobs through a comprehensive project in the Old City of Kabul reviving crafts, culture and communities. The project has five components: 1) Training artisans in practical and business skills at the Turquoise Mountain Institute, 2) conducting a mentoring programme in design, production and marketing, 3) restore historic buildings using trained local labourers, 4) pioneering model healthcare, community outreach and primary education for predominately women and youth and 5) promoting Afghan culture through national and international exhibitions and cultural events.</narrative>
  </description>
